advancements.swem.main.amethyst.descript: A mysterious purple shard. You might start to feel light-headed. Make you sure you know where home is.
advancements.swem.main.amethyst.title: Amethyst
advancements.swem.main.amethyst_boots.de: Boots laced with magic. As useful as before, but now you mustn't even fear the skies.
advancements.swem.main.amethyst_bow.desc: Its almost as if the arrows appear from nothing - wishing for you to use them.
advancements.swem.main.amethyst_chestpla: Do not fear. Move forward. Face the enemy head-on.
advancements.swem.main.amethyst_helmet.d: The air feels cleaner and easier to breathe than through your average helmet.
advancements.swem.main.amethyst_horse_ar: Im not sure what this means. Maybe you do.
advancements.swem.main.amethyst_longswor: Strike from the back of a horse with the long arm of your new authority.
advancements.swem.main.amethyst_pants.de: With a renewed vigor, you lift from your knees to fight again.
advancements.swem.main.amethyst_scythe.d: A weapon of war inspired by the fires of the farmer's hearts.
advancements.swem.main.cantazarite.descr: Workable but strong, with a sparkle of life. I wonder how many uses it has.
advancements.swem.main.cantazarite.title: Cantazarite Anvil
advancements.swem.main.cantazarite_anvil: Strong as iron, half as heavy, double the use.
advancements.swem.main.cantazarite_dye.d: It doesn't actually dye things. It must have another purpose.
advancements.swem.main.cantazarite_potio: My horse seems to be really interested in this potion.
advancements.swem.main.diamond_boots.des: Comfortable and warm, but never too hot.
advancements.swem.main.glow_boots.descri: A little bit of light for dark nights.
advancements.swem.main.glow_boots.title: Glow Riding Boots
advancements.swem.main.gold_boots.descri: The gold in my boots seems to react when I walk near water.
advancements.swem.main.gold_boots.title: Gold Riding Boots
Helping you measure your horse's jump height since 2022.
advancements.swem.main.root.title: SWEM
advancements.swem.main.shavings.descript: The care of an animal shows the character of the one who owns it.
advancements.swem.main.shavings.title: Shavings
advancements.swem.main.slow_feeders.desc: Keep their bellies from grumbling and their guts from colicing.
advancements.swem.main.star_worm_block_d: Capable AND rich. Look at you go!
advancements.swem.main.star_worm_goop.de: Glowy slime. This might be important. By that, I mean VERY important.
advancements.swem.main.tack_box.descript: Keep all your horse's belongings close by.
advancements.swem.main.tack_box.title: Tack Box
advancements.swem.main.western_barrel.de: Speed and agility are important for any equine's training.
advancements.swem.main.whistle.descripti: Call your beast to you even in the heat of battle.
advancements.swem.main.whistle.title: Whistle
